			<![CDATA[1. I told Angie, “Try again tomorrow.” 
    I told Angie to try again <blank word="the next day"/>.

2. He said, “The power outage affected many neighborhoods in the area.”
    He said that the power outage <blank word="had affected"/> many neighborhoods in the area.

3. Experts always say, “Don’t wait until the last minute.” 
    Experts always say <blank word="not to wait"/> until the last minute.

4. Channel 4 told viewers, “We provide the most up-to-date news coverage.”
    Channel 4 told viewers that they <blank word="provided"/>  the most up-to-date news coverage. 

5. The mayor told residents, “Buy emergency supplies early!”
    The mayor told residents <blank word="to buy"/> emergency supplies early.

6. Our neighbor said, “There is an official evacuation route.”
    Our neighbor said there <blank word="was"/> an official evacuation route.]]>
